wt.productfamily

Class PSBVariantSpecDefaultNavCriteriaDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • DefaultGetDefaultNavCriteriaDelegate
      • wt.productfamily.PSBVariantSpecDefaultNavCriteriaDelegate

  • public class PSBVariantSpecDefaultNavCriteriaDelegate
extends DefaultGetDefaultNavCriteriaDelegate
    Default navigation criteria delegate for Variant Spec Structure Browser. It is recommended that any custom navigation criteria delegate for Variant Spec Structure Browser extends this implementation and overrides the getDefaultNavCriteria(WTCollection, NavCriteriaContext) method to return the desired navigation criteria for Variant Spec Structure Browser.



    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
